## ğŸš€ How to Run

### 1. Install dependencies

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

You may also need Graphviz installed on your system for tree visualization:
- [https://graphviz.org/download/](https://graphviz.org/download/)

### 2. Run the project

```bash
python main.py
```

